lead_paragraph: Italian import Matteo Mancosu struck again on Sunday with a second-half goal to lift the Montreal Impact over the New York Red Bulls 1-0 in the first leg of the Eastern Conference semi-finals at Stade Saputo in Montreal.

headline.print_headline: Italian Mancosu Continues Major Impact for Montreal
